Modifications made for speculators framework integration:
- Adapted architecture to speculators framework patterns
- Added configuration classes with Pydantic validation
- Integrated with speculators registry and proposal systems
- Enhanced error handling and generation parameters
- Added comprehensive type hints and documentation
- Implemented framework-specific verifier attachment
- Added support for various generation configurations

